title: GOOP DAO Proposal #3
body:
YES Vote:

-Minimum bid of 69.69 indefinitely on every Noun while treasury multisig has at least that much in funds; until a Noun is acquired.
-Authorization of max funds per Noun; until a Noun is acquired.
-Once Noun is acquired, create new proposal on bidding procedure.

NO Vote:

-Hold all funds until new proposal is passed.
